    MenuBarController
    Controller for MenuBar.fxml initializes data for the application.
    ReportsController
    Controller for the Reports view nested in Scheduler's TabPane.
    ScheduleController
    Controller class for the Schedule.fxml that holds the tab pane for the other views and the MenuBar.
    Scheduler
    Scheduler class is a container for all model objects and has a few methods to complete required application setup.
    UpdateAppointmentFormController
    Class to control the Update Appointment Form.
    UpdateCustomerFormController
    Class to control the Update Customer Form.

    UserDao
    User Data Access Interface for CRUD operations on persistence layer.
    UserImpl
    Queries the mySql database with CRUD operations for the User model object.
